            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1359982476,
            "creation_date": 1359982476,
            "body": "<p>Another alternative is AndroidSVG (<a href=\"http://code.google.com/p/androidsvg/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://code.google.com/p/androidsvg/<\/a>).<\/p>\n",
